body.p:
The "Pennsylvania" System of Academic Costume, appearing for the first time on this
occasion, indicates Faculties and Degrees as follows--FACULTIES: Arts, marine blue;
Philosophy, sapphire blue; Science, light blue; Music, very light blue; Law,
purple; Medicine, crimson; Dentistry, pink; Veterinary Medicine,
cardinal. DEGREES: Undergraduate, cord; Bachelor, yoke;
Master or Doctor, yoke and border, in Faculty color.
